1
00:00:01,040 --> 00:00:08,920
The end of winter is always uncertain.
And then spring, hiding in the cold wind,

2
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:14,799
suddenly lifts its head.
I’m like that too.

3
00:00:14,799 --> 00:00:22,240
The feelings I’ve forced down
start blooming again whenever I see you.

4
00:00:22,240 --> 00:00:27,000
You don’t know.
Every time I call your name, my heart

5
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:34,880
starts racing,
and when you smile, my whole day feels okay.

6
00:00:35,079 --> 00:00:39,760
Pretending I’m fine has always been the easiest thing.

7
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:45,371
Especially in front of you.

8
00:00:45,371 --> 00:00:47,205
Fifteen years.

9
00:00:48,336 --> 00:00:54,451
Same road.
Same distance.

10
00:00:54,451 --> 00:01:01,301
All that time—
behind you, beside you, watching you.

11
00:01:01,301 --> 00:01:08,400
Now I don’t want to just face the same direction—
I want to stand at the same eye level.

12
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,554
This year… I’m ending it.

13
00:01:10,554 --> 00:01:12,991
This one-sided love.

14
00:01:12,991 --> 00:01:17,885
I want to become someone special to you.

15
00:01:18,418 --> 00:01:21,533
Yujin.

16
00:01:23,079 --> 00:01:26,720
Congratulations on graduating, Yujin.

17
00:01:33,399 --> 00:01:39,439
How have you been?
Sorry—I’m a bit late.

18
00:01:40,399 --> 00:01:45,000
I can’t believe our Yujin is graduating already.
I’m—

19
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:49,640
I’m kind of emotional.
Graduation already…

20
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:55,691
It’s about time, honestly.
Seo Yujin—am I invisible to you or what?

21
00:01:55,691 --> 00:01:59,439
Oh—hey. You’re here?

22
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:03,560
I ran into Yuho out front.

23
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:12,000
Let’s take a picture too.
Okay—say cheese.

24
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:16,800
One, two, three.

25
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:29,720
This time, the three of us together.

26
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:46,720
When did you get this big?
Alright—let’s go eat something good.

27
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:50,560
By the way, did you find someone to hire?

28
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:53,720
Not yet.
Ugh, you’ll be busy—you should find someone soon.

29
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:19,080
Oh, and this—
this is your graduation gift, Yujin.

30
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:28,959
Wow… Yujin’s so lucky.

31
00:03:29,799 --> 00:03:34,959
Thank you so much, hyung.
I’m gonna wear it every day.

32
00:03:34,959 --> 00:03:40,920
Yeah.

33
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:45,280
I’ll say it now—about your café…
what if I worked there and helped you out?

34
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:48,920
I want to.
You’d help? Yujin?

35
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:55,519
You’re a freshman now—won’t it be too much?
I’ll manage my schedule so school won’t suffer.

36
00:03:55,519 --> 00:03:58,720
I’ll handle it.

37
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:03,720
Yeah, put him to work while you can.
Use him.

38
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:09,640
I’d love it if you came.
But if it gets tough, tell me anytime.

39
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:13,959
Okay?
Yeah.

40
00:04:18,799 --> 00:04:25,160
Take care, Taeyoon.
Thanks for driving us. Get home safe.

41
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:31,720
Yujin, see you tomorrow.
Yeah. Drive safely.

42
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:35,520
I’ll come by tomorrow.
You won’t be able to sleep tonight from excitement,

43
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:40,919
will you?
Maybe I won’t.

44
00:04:40,919 --> 00:04:45,297
So you’re not even trying to hide it anymore.

45
00:04:45,297 --> 00:04:54,080
You know, noona—how long I’ve waited.
I know. That’s why I’m more worried.

46
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:58,280
If Taeyoon…
Ah—never mind.

47
00:04:58,280 --> 00:05:03,120
Don’t worry too much. I’m really going to try.
And one reason he could reject me is gone now.

48
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:06,240
I’m an adult now.

49
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:10,199
Yeah… how could I possibly stop you?

50
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:15,280
Oh my god. Our cute youngest.

51
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:22,560
Seriously. Stop treating me like a kid.

52
00:05:24,479 --> 00:05:27,125
You little cutie.

53
00:05:27,125 --> 00:05:29,284
Come on, let’s go.

54
00:05:34,319 --> 00:05:40,440
Yujin…
you really are all grown up now.

55
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:52,360
Taeyoon hyung.

56
00:05:54,039 --> 00:05:57,759
Let’s take a picture together.

57
00:05:58,160 --> 00:06:03,039
Back then…
you were really adorable.

58
00:06:03,039 --> 00:06:08,240
Not that you aren’t pretty now too, Yujin.

59
00:06:15,287 --> 00:06:15,861
Hyung…

60
00:06:16,053 --> 00:06:19,025
Yujin, wake up.

61
00:06:19,025 --> 00:06:21,029
Hey—Seo Yujin.

62
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,987
What?
You already left?

63
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:46,769
Yujin, why are you here so early?

64
00:06:47,729 --> 00:06:53,174
I wanted to learn the job from you…
so I came a little early.

65
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:58,000
Look at you—so diligent.

66
00:06:58,080 --> 00:07:00,390
Want a cup of coffee, Yujin?

67
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:04,566
Hello. Oh—Yujin! Hello.

68
00:07:04,566 --> 00:07:08,806
Yujin’s going to help out for a while.

69
00:07:08,806 --> 00:07:14,240
Boss, I guess we’re going to get even busier.

70
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:25,479
It really suits you.
You look so good.

71
00:07:25,479 --> 00:07:29,599
I love it too. Thank you, hyung.

72
00:07:29,599 --> 00:07:36,720
Alright then—shall we start making coffee?

73
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:48,400
It’s not about strength—
balance matters.

74
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:32,680
Maybe it’s because you made it, Yujin…
It’s good.

75
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:37,200
Hyung.
Here.

76
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:56,309
I guess I ate it a little too enthusiastically.

77
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:10,519
It was your first day—tiring, right?
You worked really hard.

78
00:09:10,519 --> 00:09:13,204
I’ll drive you home. Come on.

79
00:09:14,462 --> 00:09:20,631
Yujin’s really good at this.
You learn fast.

80
00:09:20,631 --> 00:09:23,255
Making coffee was fun.

81
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:25,311
Hyung…

82
00:09:26,186 --> 00:09:27,952
Have you been sleeping okay lately?

83
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:37,720
I’m okay. Thanks for worrying.
If you can’t sleep, call me.

84
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,586
I’ll listen—anytime.

85
00:09:40,141 --> 00:09:44,633
Having you around… really helps.

86
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:52,491
I wish you’d rely on me completely.

87
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:58,895
After we’re done tomorrow…
want to grab a drink with me?

88
00:09:58,895 --> 00:10:00,824
Yeah. I’d like that.

89
00:10:03,399 --> 00:10:05,000
Then see you tomorrow. Sleep well.

90
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:10,013
You too—get home safe. See you tomorrow.
